# NAME: TikTok
# AUTHOR: Codex
# UPDATED: 2026-06-13
# FORMAT: Surge Ruleset
# SOURCES: TikTok for Developers, SukkaW/Surge, blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script, Rabbit-Spec/Surge
# NOTE: TikTok international app, web, account/API, video, image, effect and live-media traffic.
# NOTE: Other ByteDance products, generic telemetry, shared cloud ranges and volatile IPs are intentionally excluded.

# TikTok-specific host on a shared effect CDN domain
DOMAIN,lf16-effectcdn.byteeffecttos-g.com

# International control plane and media delivery
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,byteintlapi.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,byteoversea.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ibytedtos.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ibyteimg.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ipstatp.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,isnssdk.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,muscdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,musical.ly
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,sgpstatp.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tik-tokapi.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktok.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktok.us
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokapis.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokcdn-us.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokcdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokd.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokd.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokv.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokv.us
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tiktokw.com

# Dynamic TikTok Akamai host family, such as p16-tiktokcdn-com.akamaized.net
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,-tiktokcdn-com

# HTTP/HTTPS client fallback
USER-AGENT,TikTok*
